'''Final Fantasy IV''' (released as '''Final Fantasy II''' in North America) is a landmark SNES RPG introducing the Active Time Battle system.

==Overview==

Revolutionary features:
* Active Time Battle (ATB) system - first implementation
* Character-driven narrative
* Class-based party system
* Multiple worlds to explore

